Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Class LitmusAssertionsBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen.LitmusAssertionsBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
LitmusAssertionsListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class LitmusAssertionsBaseListener extends Object implements LitmusAssertionsListener
This class provides an empty implementation of LitmusAssertionsListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
